&lt;p&gt;RPM Packaging for OpenStack is an cross-distribution and cross-vendor effort to create common templates for building OpenStack packages for RPM based Linux and OpenStack distributions. The project was started with the goal of unifying the independent packaging efforts of RDO and SUSE, but is really open for anyone who wants to contribute RPM packaging spec files for any distribution.&lt;/p&gt;
