      <title>Ruby2.4.x rpm安装包制作</title>
      <link>https://www.xiexianbin.cn/linux/rpm/2018-01-02-ruby-rpm-2-4-x/index.html</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2018 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.xiexianbin.cn/linux/rpm/2018-01-02-ruby-rpm-2-4-x/</guid>
